{"tid":412763,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話說頭先係又一城爆石...","createTime":"2017-09-25T02:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T05:28:01.000Z","uid":145101,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1276aa2fd2a90803d4d14b9248b968e4b26b1dad","tid":412763,"uid":145101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:57:13.000Z","msg":"今朝個肚痛到爆炸<br />\n急急忙忙衝左去又一城個廁所爆石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痾出黎個下真係爽撚到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲屎baba聲咁傾瀉而出<br />\n雖然真係好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   但係臭到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n抺乾淨屁股臨走個陣先發現個廁所沖唔到水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個下我真係好徬徨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  試多幾次個自動沖廁都係唔得<br />\n平時最撚憎啲人去完廁所唔沖廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係估唔到今次係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後我決定合埋個廁所板<br />\n等啲屎冇咁大陣臭味<br />\n出到去廁格仲擔心有人會啤住我冇沖廁<br />\n如果有邊位巴打咁好彩入到我個格千祈唔好怪我<br />\n我都唔想架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n估唔到係連登第一個post係講屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d969c1c023cd1e84583aafb33822a9142d61f38e","tid":412763,"uid":145101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif